     <div id="content"> 
      <div id="latestnews"> 
       <h2></h2> 
       <ul> 
        <li> <p>This Website contains essential information for undergraduates of the University of Colombo. This website was prepared with the intention of providing you with a helping hand, in order to enrich your University life. The Student Counsellors’ Office is committed to provide you with means, guidance and counselling to resolve problems you encounter in your day-to-day University life. This document contains all required information about what steps to take when faced with difficulties in the student life. </p> </li> 
       </ul> 
      </div> 
